OL,3,CProtest laws based on 'kneejerk public
OL,4,Copinion', says think tank
OL,6,FThe Government should review
OL,7,Flegislation that restricts protest
OL,8,Fbased on "knee-jerk public opinion", a
OL,9,Fthink tank has said.
OL,11,FCross-party think tank Demos said it
OL,12,Fhad found "overwhelming support" for
OL,13,Fthe right to protest, saying the
OL,14,Fpublic's views were "more nuanced"
OL,15,Fthan simply being concerned about
OL,16,Fdisruption.
