OL,3,CProtest laws based on 'kneejerk public
OL,4,Copinion', says think tank
OL,6,FIn a report published on Thursday
OL,7,Falongside civil rights campaigners
OL,8,FLiberty, Demos called for a "wide-
OL,9,Franging" independent review of protest
OL,10,Flegislation and the policing of
OL,11,Fprotest.
OL,13,FThe report followed a series of
OL,14,Fdeliberative workshops held by Demos,
OL,15,Fwhich the think tank said gave members
OL,16,Fof the public more time and
OL,17,Finformation to reach "properly
OL,18,Fconsidered judgements" that saw
OL,19,Fconcerns about disruption become "less
OL,20,Fprominent".
