OL,3,CProtest laws based on 'kneejerk public
OL,4,Copinion', says think tank
OL,6,FThe report follows a series of laws
OL,7,Fpassed by the previous government that
OL,8,Fcreated a new offence of intentionally
OL,9,For recklessly causing public nuisance,
OL,10,Fwith a maximum sentence of 10 years.
OL,12,FThe previous government also gave the
OL,13,Fpolice new powers to crack down on
OL,14,Fnoisy protests and those causing
OL,15,F"serious disruption" amid anger at
OL,16,Fongoing protests by environmental
OL,17,Fgroups such as Just Stop Oil and
OL,18,FInsulate Britain.
