OL,3,CProtest laws based on 'kneejerk public
OL,4,Copinion', says think tank
OL,6,FIn July, five Just Stop Oil activists
OL,7,Fwere jailed under the new laws for
OL,8,Fbetween four and five years for
OL,9,Forganising a protest intended to cause
OL,10,Fgridlock on the M25.
OL,12,FAkiko Hart, director of Liberty, said
OL,13,Flegislation "fuelled by inflammatory
OL,14,Frhetoric" had "weakened our right to
OL,15,Fprotest".
