OL,3,CProtest laws based on 'kneejerk public
OL,4,Copinion', says think tank
OL,6,FShe said: "Rather than seeking to
OL,7,Fengage with protesters, we saw the
OL,8,Fprevious government choose to bring in
OL,9,Fever more extreme legislation which
OL,10,Fheavily restricts protests through
OL,11,Fimpractical measures that needlessly
OL,12,Ffunnel thousands of protesters into
OL,13,Fthe criminal justice system.
OL,15,F"These unworkable laws were brought in
OL,16,Fas a reaction to particular protests
OL,17,Fbut make it harder for all of us, no
OL,18,Fmatter our cause, to stand up to
OL,19,Fpower."
